This subtitle applies only in the following counties:
Allegany County;
Baltimore County, including motorcycles located on any of the places enumerated in § 19-301 of this subtitle, unless authorized;
Calvert County;
Caroline County;
Carroll County, including motorcycles located on any of the places enumerated in § 19-301 of this subtitle, unless authorized;
Cecil County;
Charles County;
Dorchester County;
Frederick County;
Garrett County;
Harford County;
Howard County;
Montgomery County;
Prince George's County;
St. Mary's County;
Somerset County; and
Wicomico County.
